OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud, rain
OL,6,For drizzle moves southeastwards,
OL,7,Freaching most areas by dawn, though
OL,8,Fthe far southeast staying dry. Clearer
OL,9,Fspells and frequent showers follow
OL,10,Ffrom the northwest, these wintry over
OL,11,Fthe Scottish hills. Increasingly windy
OL,12,Fwith coastal gales affecting northern
OL,13,FScotland.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FCloudy and breezy across
OL,16,FEngland and Wales with outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain gradually clearing southwards.
OL,18,FSunny spells and showers elsewhere,
OL,19,Fthese wintry over some northern hills.
OL,20,FFeeling chilly in the wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
